This page is about me!
My name is Madison Kroum.
I am a Senior graduating from Texas A&M University this December.
My major is Communication and I am getting my minor in English.
An interesting fact about me is that my sisters and I were each named after U.S. Presidents: Madison, Kennedy, and Reagan.
